{"tid":1900252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【拋磚引玉】加速派發一萬蚊","createTime":"2020-02-27T06:20:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T10:32:35.000Z","uid":62721,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1e53a926b9cb89e4f541be9db393d8439716d19e","tid":1900252,"uid":62721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T06:20:18.000Z","msg":"政府呢次出招綁一萬蚊同黑警撥款係財政預算<br />\n深水埗廢老聽到有一萬蚊幾鬼開心（詳情睇下有線）<br />\n好多基層甚至淺黃都係咁諗，依加反對即係係佢銀包拎走一萬蚊，財政預算=一萬蚊<br />\n因為政府企係道德高地用基層民意夾鳩議員<br />\n民主派點投都死，少數派又呃到9月選票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係唔可以贊成同反對底下，拆解方法只有一個，提出反建議，打民意戰<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mOaBh7t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmOaBh7t.jpg&h=69cdf988&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">加快派發一萬蚊，比政府企係更加高嘅道德高地</span></span><br />\n議員提議案/建議，要求政府係一兩個月內派發一萬蚊，<strong>真正急市民所急</strong> ，筆錢可以係已經批左嘅抗疫基金出<br />\n到時政府同少數派嘅論述即時瓦解，試想像下少數派俾人問支唔支持市民提早收錢，唔洗等到下年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n深水埗廢老又開心，話早應該係咁啦， 4000蚊都等左咁耐，又9up 話等住果一萬買口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由係基層銀包拎走一萬蚊變成加快塞錢落錢佢袋<br />\n9月嘅選票就唔洗擔心<br />\n議員應該由呢一刻起唔好再提咩黑警撥款，要用建制Tone直接話會反對派錢派咁慢財政預算，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大力支持加速派錢！！</span><br />\n<br />\n拋磚引玉，想研究下議事規則有冇得提出議案，先過財政預算表決"},{"pid":"1e1fb344000729e49267c98751991931868ae392","tid":1900252,"uid":62721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T06:22:08.000Z","msg":"仲可以提埋免申請，要降低行政費之類<br />\n誠哥都可以係一個月內派到錢啦，政府唔通要一年？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bb59b7eaa142088f7c41291db18d537a9fefa65","tid":1900252,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T06:25:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推!!"},{"pid":"c12aec7fc0ed89cbbb5e39dc64855af98cab6988","tid":1900252,"uid":62721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T06:27:14.000Z","msg":"睇完幫手推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60acfefb103892b100c8c809cd8866e6fda51277","tid":1900252,"uid":62721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T06:32:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0d8d6fc4850153883b3fd8080a7594334b4df3f","tid":1900252,"uid":62721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T06:41:07.000Z","msg":"呢個方法絕對好過就咁贊成或者反對"},{"pid":"13edf14ccf795c817d134d0b51b4dfec0030364e","tid":1900252,"uid":38891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T06:45:42.000Z","msg":"反對完<br />\n之後出post話支持<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學民建聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b3f69e23fab649a776aedeacef1b8f93ed763a2","tid":1900252,"uid":62721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13edf14ccf795c817d134d0b51b4dfec0030364e","tid":1900252,"uid":38891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T06:45:42.000Z","msg":"反對完<br />\n之後出post話支持<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學民建聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T06:58:05.000Z","msg":"依加邊個民主派話反對派一萬蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56122a79606574ab3f3a357c760534f4c547dca2","tid":1900252,"uid":62721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s